<concept id="concept_1BCF5C425D7D4627AB1C66A085CF6E11" xml:lang="en-us">
            <title>Controlling the Provisioning Process</title>
            <conbody>
                        <section>
                                    <p>The <ph audience="aws">AWS</ph><ph audience="os">OpenStack</ph><ph
                                                            audience="vmware">vSphere</ph><ph audience="azure"
                                                            >Azure</ph> integration provides you with the following feature for controlling the <ph
                                                            audience="aws"
                                                            >provisioning and deprovisioning of virtual servers:</ph><ph
                                                            audience="os"
                                                            >provisioning and deprovisioning of virtual systems:</ph><ph
                                                            audience="vmware"
                                                            >provisioning, modification, and deprovisioning of VMs:</ph>
                                    </p>
                                    <p>In the definition of the technical services for <ph audience="aws">AWS</ph><ph
                                                            audience="os">OpenStack</ph><ph audience="vmware"
                                                            >vSphere</ph><ph audience="azure"
                                                            >Azure</ph>, you can specify the<codeph> MAIL_FOR_COMPLETION</codeph> parameter. This is an address to which emails are to be sent <ph
                                                            audience="aws"
                                                            >describing manual steps required to complete an operation</ph><ph
                                                            audience="os"
                                                            >describing manual steps required to complete an operation</ph><ph
                                                            audience="vmware"
                                                            >in case manual steps are required to complete an operation</ph>. </p>
                                    <p>If you specify this parameter, the <ph audience="aws">AWS</ph><ph audience="os"
                                                            >OpenStack</ph><ph audience="vmware">VMware</ph><ph
                                                            audience="azure"
                                                >Azure</ph> service controller interrupts the processing of each operation before its completion and waits for a notification about the execution of a manual action. This notification consists in opening the link given in the email. </p>
                                    <p>Omit the <codeph>MAIL_FOR_COMPLETION</codeph> parameter if you do not want to interrupt the processing. </p>
                        </section>
            </conbody>
</concept>
